{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2e3d638c0a","title":"周恩来关于召开国庆大会等问题给新疆的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"320db26f53","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":1,"articleId":"2e3d638c0a"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"ee21afb82f","name":"新疆文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fcdd4e890d","type":"title","text":"周恩来关于召开国庆大会等问题给新疆的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2e3d638c0a"},{"id":"3695c7ce62","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2e3d638c0a"},{"id":"40deacd9d1","type":"appellation","text":"〖时间：上午，总理来电指示（要点）〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2e3d638c0a"},{"id":"7fdd986b72","type":"paragraph","text":"一，都不要在人民广场开会；","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2e3d638c0a"},{"id":"5519614ab3","type":"paragraph","text":"二，新疆军区，军区生产建设兵团、七三三五部队自己开；","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2e3d638c0a"},{"id":"62574cc53a","type":"paragraph","text":"三，红二司在南门体育场开；","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2e3d638c0a"},{"id":"c8cb6c92cc","type":"paragraph","text":"四，工农革委会等自己找地方开。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2e3d638c0a"},{"id":"2e65e3cbad","type":"paragraph","text":"（注）：关于召开国庆大会，我三新革命造反派遵照总理指示，积极准备参加军区的大会（当然也有不少战士思想不通），但是，死不悔改的走资派王恩茂一小撮制造了骇人听闻的“九·二八”惨案。当时中央考虑到在一起开会可能发生问题，决定分开庆祝。这样又出现了会场问题，都想在人民广场开会，争持不下，所以总理就作了如上四点指示。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2e3d638c0a"}],"page":{"id":"e908e19802","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2e3d638c0a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}